ticorrelation between the core asymmetry and the Dopplershift, suggesting a\nchange of the core asymmetry from redward to blueward with an increasing\nredshift of the Halpha core. The data and the applied analysis do not show\nmeaningful tracks of Alfven waves in the selected network element.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Apr 2013 09:27:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-27"}
