zed second-order\nperturbation theory (rPT2). Finally, the improved description of dipole moments\nfor a small set of diatomic molecules demonstrates the quality of the sc-GW\nground state density.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Apr 2013 10:05:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Aug 2013 14:32:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-12"}
