 S-F interface especially in the ferromagnetic side,\nshowing a spin-glass-like magnetic state. Our findings reveal that the\nproximity effect in the superconductor-d0 ferromagnet heterostructures will\nprovide the knowledge and basis to enhance the Tc value of the existing\nsuperconductors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Apr 2013 14:01:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Sep 2019 06:52:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 2 Oct 2020 07:56:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-05"}
